{"tid":1931032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：武漢病毒自古以來是中國的病毒，任何武獨主張皆違反全國人民意願，外國勢力陰謀最終不會得逞","createTime":"2020-03-18T03:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T12:48:49.000Z","uid":159913,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a248962128c2d4f789fdc7bd9d01b0afea283355","tid":1931032,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"中國武漢病毒（簡稱中國病毒/武漢病毒）眾所周知是起源於中國武漢市的強大生化武器。最近國際有論調試圖將武漢從中國分離出去，甚至對武漢採取去中國化處理，嚴重違反「一個中國」原則，對此中方表示強烈抗議！<br />\n<br />\n我國外交部多次重申，任何試圖將武漢從偉大祖國分離的外國陰謀皆不會得逞。我國在維護領土完整的決心一直堅定，絕不容許武漢脫離中國存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35684643de3bc41b646693c99739221b8b526d8a","tid":1931032,"uid":49336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"望望個名 唔係老衲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b474d707dbec44e931881f1a6f79eef69ec4646d","tid":1931032,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"反對武漢獨立，堅決維護領土完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399159d5602e7e8dfab1c68b0bb40914b9257b47","tid":1931032,"uid":159913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35684643de3bc41b646693c99739221b8b526d8a","tid":1931032,"uid":49336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"望望個名 唔係老衲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"老衲作風敗壞違反黨紀，已被依法雙規<br />\n人民日報社論以後由我打骰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4647ade8f90dba5621f7065898249cd1157597","tid":1931032,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61ea950752165fed73765b134b55a6b5cb86426","tid":1931032,"uid":159913,"like":0,